---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Compliance Services | Bluebonnet CyberWorks">
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="text-center max-w-4xl mx-auto mb-16 px-4">
    <h1 class="text-5xl font-extrabold text-blue-900 leading-tight mb-6">
      Compliance Made Simple
    </h1>
    <p class="text-xl text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
      Bluebonnet CyberWorks helps organizations meet today’s toughest cybersecurity standards—
      with clarity, confidence, and expert guidance. Whether you're aiming for PCI-DSS, HIPAA, or NIST 800-171 compliance,
      we’ll walk with you every step of the way.
    </p>
  </section>

  <!-- Services Grid -->
  <section class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4">
    <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-2xl shadow-sm p-6 hover:shadow-md transition">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-blue-800 mb-2">PCI-DSS Compliance</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700 text-base leading-relaxed">
        We help merchants and service providers meet the 12 core PCI requirements through tailored gap assessments,
        remediation plans, and policy creation.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-2xl shadow-sm p-6 hover:shadow-md transition">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-blue-800 mb-2">NIST 800-171</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700 text-base leading-relaxed">
        For contractors and academic institutions handling CUI, we offer System Security Plans (SSP), POA&Ms,
        and control implementation support.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-2xl shadow-sm p-6 hover:shadow-md transition">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-blue-800 mb-2">HIPAA & HITECH</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700 text-base leading-relaxed">
        We guide healthcare practices, vendors, and covered entities through the HIPAA Security & Privacy Rules
        with practical policies and risk assessments.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-2xl shadow-sm p-6 hover:shadow-md transition">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-blue-800 mb-2">CMMC Readiness</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700 text-base leading-relaxed">
        Whether you're preparing for Level 1 or Level 2 certification, we help align your environment with
        CMMC expectations using NIST-based practices.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Call to Action -->
  <section class="text-center mt-20 mb-12 px-4">
    <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-4">
      Unsure where to start with compliance?
    </h3>
    <p class="text-base text-gray-600 mb-6">
      Book a free 30-minute consultation to discuss your goals and get clarity on your compliance journey.
    </p>
    <a
      href="/contact"
      class="inline-block bg-blue-800 text-white font-medium text-lg px-6 py-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-blue-700 transition"
    >
      Request a Free Consultation
    </a>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
